snippet.title: Wild Assault Official Trailer: Assemble
snippet.description:
This is a long overdue self-introduction. 
A gift to #WildAssault players and our community from Combat Cat Studio. 
From here, the Wild Assault universe unfolds. 
Now we present you the Wild Assault Official Trailer: Assemble!
——————————————————————————
Wild Assault Beta Test: Assemble starts on July 31.
Add to your wishlist NOW: bit.ly/WildAssault
Join our official Discord: discord.gg/wildassault
See you in Operation Mojave ❤️🫡
————————————————————————————————————————
😼 Wild Assault is a Furry Tactical Shooter developed with Unreal Engine 5! 
Check it out on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2827230/Wild_Assault/
🐰 Follow us on social media!
